    function shopAjaxGet (options) {
        var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest()
        xhr.open('GET', options.url, true)
        xhr.timeout = options.timeout
        xhr.onreadystatechange = function () {
            if (xhr.readyState === 4) {
                var status = xhr.status

                if (status === 0 && !(xhr.responseURL && xhr.responseURL.indexOf('file:') === 0)) {
                    return
                }

                var response
                if (status >= 200 && status < 300) {
                    var type = xhr.getResponseHeader('Content-type') || 'application/json'
                    if (type.indexOf('xml') !== -1 && xhr.responseXML) {
                        response = xhr.responseXML
                    } else if (type.indexOf('json') > -1) {
                        try {
                            response = JSON.parse(xhr.responseText)
                        } catch (e) {
                            response = ''
                        }
                    } else {
                        response = xhr.responseText
                    }
                    options.success && options.success(response)
                } else {
                    var err = new Error('Request failed with status code ' + xhr.status)
                    options.error && options.error(err)
                }
            }
        }
        xhr.onerror = function() {
            var err = new Error('Network Error')
            options.error && options.error(err)
        }
        xhr.onabort = function() {
            var err = new Error('Request aborted')
            options.error && options.error(err)
        }
        xhr.ontimeout = function() {
            var err = new Error('timeout of ' + timeout + 'ms exceeded')
            options.error && options.error(err)
        }
        xhr.withCredentials = true
        xhr.setRequestHeader('Accept', 'application/json, text/plain, */*')
        xhr.send()
    }

    function asyncAll () {
        var argsList = Array.prototype.slice.call(arguments);
        var asyncList = argsList.slice(0, argsList.length - 1);
        var callback = argsList[argsList.length - 1];

        var count = 0;
        var responses = [];
        asyncList.forEach(function (asyncItem, index) {
            asyncItem(function (res) {
                count++;
                responses[index] = res;
                if (count === asyncList.length) {
                    callback(responses);
                }
            });
        });
    }

    function gotoHomeOld() {
        // 调用多个异步请求，等全都返回时再执行 callback
        asyncAll(function(callback) {
            var scriptNode = document.createElement('script');
            var callbackName = 'jsonpCB_' + Date.now() + '_' + Math.random().toString(36).substr(2);
            window[callbackName] = function() {
                delete window[callbackName];
                document.body.removeChild(scriptNode);
                callback();

            }
            scriptNode.src = '//passport.shop.jd.com/json/navigation/changeStyle.action?style=vcStyle&callback=' + callbackName;
            document.body.appendChild(scriptNode);
        }, function(callback) {
            shopAjaxGet({
                url: 'https://vchebe.jd.com/userlog/userSwitchClick?type=20',
                timeout: 2000,
                success: function() {
                    callback('');
                },
                error: function() {
                    callback('');
                }
            });
        }, function() {
            window.location.href = '//vcp.jd.com';
        })

    };

    function gotoOld() {
        // 调用多个异步请求，等全都返回时再执行 callback
        asyncAll(function(callback) {
            var scriptNode = document.createElement('script');
            var callbackName = 'jsonpCB_' + Date.now() + '_' + Math.random().toString(36).substr(2);
            var currentUrl =  window.location.href;
            var pos = currentUrl.search("_source")
            if(pos!=-1){
                currentUrl = currentUrl.slice(0,pos-1);
            }
            window[callbackName] = function() {
                delete window[callbackName];
                document.body.removeChild(scriptNode);
                callback(currentUrl);
                window.location.href = currentUrl;
            }
            scriptNode.src = '//passport.shop.jd.com/json/navigation/changeStyle.action?style=vcStyle&callback=' + callbackName;
            document.body.appendChild(scriptNode);
        }, function(callback) {
            shopAjaxGet({
                url: 'https://vchebe.jd.com/userlog/userSwitchClick?type=20',
                timeout: 2000,
                success: function() {
                    callback('');
                },
                error: function() {
                    callback('');
                }
            });
        }, function(responses) {
            window.location.href = responses[0];
        })
    };
